      <strong>Looking Forward</strong><br><br>
      Upon deployment, Treasury users will be able to move away from the legacy system and towards this enterprise system with <p class="channel-orange">increased capacity and navigability.</p> As a result, they spend less time compiling data from different sources and <p class="channel-orange">more time analyzing those data to use bond proceeds as effectively as possible.</p>
    </div>
